precis:
Enactment of the QUALIFICATIONS FOR DESIGNATIONS AS ANALYSTS REGULATIONS
which prescribe the qualifications that a person must possess to be
designated by the Minister as an analyst for the purposes of the Act and
Regulations, to ensure that only qualified individuals are designated as
analysts.
